---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-brand-dark py-16 px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-12">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <span class="text-brand-dark text-xs font-bold font-heading">FL</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-lg font-heading tracking-wider text-white leading-none">FLORALAB</span>
            <span class="text-[11px] font-sans tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 uppercase leading-none mt-1">Education</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-sm max-w-xs mt-4">
          Школа флористики та декору. Навчаємо створювати красу власноруч.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 sm:gap-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Навчання</h4>
          <a href="/stvorennya-florariumu" class="text-white/60 text-sm hover:text-brand-lime transition-colors">Флораріуми</a>
          <a href="/kartini-zi-stabilizovanih-roslin" class="text-white/60 text-sm hover:text-brand-lime transition-colors">Картини з моху</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Контакти</h4>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/floralab" class="text-white/60 text-sm hover:text-brand-lime transition-colors">Instagram</a>
          <a href="https://t.me/floralab" class="text-white/60 text-sm hover:text-brand-lime transition-colors">Telegram</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="h-px bg-white/10 w-full my-12"></div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 text-white/20 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
      <p>© {year} Floralab Education. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
